    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition and represents the pinnacle of its model's upkeep. It has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and shows virtually no signs of use. The exterior paint is original and flawless, free of any imperfections or swirl marks. Inside, the interior is immaculate, with the leather and trim appearing brand new. Every mechanical component has been maintained to the highest standard, and the car drives flawlessly with all systems functioning exactly as they should. This is a showroom-quality vehicle suitable for the most discerning collector.",
